Aluminum Curtain Walls Market Size
Aluminum curtain walls are an exterior building facade system that consists of pre-fabricated aluminum panels and frames. The market research report for aluminum curtain walls is segmented based on type, application, region, and market players. The types include stick-built, semi-unitized, and unitized curtain walls and the applications include commercial, public, and residential buildings. The report analyzes the market players, such as JiangHong Group, Grandland Group, Yuanda China, Oldcastle BuildingEnvelope, Apogee Enterprises, China Aviation Sanxin, Kawneer, China Fangda Group, Aluprof, Vitra Scrl, Aluk Group, Zhongshan Shengxing, G.James Glass & Aluminium, Raico, Reynaers, PETRA Aluminium, Alumil, Alutech, EFCO, GUTMANN, HansenGroup, Heroal, and Permasteelisa. The report also focuses on the regulatory and legal factors that are specific to the aluminum curtain walls market conditions. These factors include building codes, environmental regulations, safety regulations, and labor laws in the regions of North America, Asia Pacific, Middle East, Africa, Australia, and Europe.

